# NSApplication.DelegateReply.failure

**Case**

Indicates an error occurred processing the operation.

## Declaration

```swift
case failure
```

## Constants

- **NSApplication.DelegateReply.success**: Indicates the operation succeeded.
- **NSApplication.DelegateReply.cancel**: Indicates the user cancelled the operation.
